TopicTitle: Airbus A350 maiden flight live stream

Articles.Content:
Hello aviation enthusiasts!

Tomorrow, on Friday, the 14th of June, the A350 will take off for the first time, and reach the most important milestone in any aircraft construction process.

The whole event will be live streamed at www.a350xwbfirstflight.com. The stream will start at 7:00 AM UTC.

Good luck to the pilots and everyone involved!

http://www.a350xwbfirstflight.com/secondary/

Just in case your browser does not redirect you.

PS: I find your lack of video quality disturbing, Airbus.

What's the EOBT?

I don't know. The take off was at 08:00 UTC.
